Subject: emacsclient: read should always return unsave and outdated
Message-Id: <b0b4445e15f3a30b-0-artemis@nixos-framework>
resolution: fixed

We cache buffer metadata to avoid sending it over and over to the LLM. However,
I think the 'unsaved' and 'outdated' fields should be sent every time, to stop
the LLM getting confused about whether it saved its changes or not.
